item.description:
OpenEMR, the most popular open-source electronic health record (EHR) and medical practice management solution, has launched OpenEMR Cloud Standard Edition in AWS Marketplace.
&ldquo;OpenEMR Cloud Standard is the first EHR in the Amazon Marketplace directly aimed at domestic US providers,&rdquo; said Asher Densmore-Lynn, an OpenEMR architect. &ldquo;We&rsquo;ve leaned on Amazon&rsquo;s orchestration services and our own state-of-the-art deployment practices to provide robust, direct answers to HIPAA&rsquo;s challenges.&rdquo;
OpenEMR Cloud Standard is the HIPAA-eligible, Marketplace edition of the OpenEMR Cloud product line.
